sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant W as Web App
    participant A as Auth Service
    participant D as Database
    U->>W: Login request
    W->>A: Validate credentials
    A->>D: Query user
    D-->>A: User record
    alt valid credentials
        A-->>W: Auth token
        W-->>U: Dashboard
    else invalid
        A-->>W: 401 Unauthorized
        W-->>U: Error message
    end
